  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/7a08d5e2557044dbc433decdafb2c2d4.poster.avif?t=1572315748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/7a08d5e2557044dbc433decdafb2c2d4.webm?t=1572315748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/7a08d5e2557044dbc433decdafb2c2d4.mp4?t=1572315748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of FILO, the unreasonably angry robot, pick up trash, throw it at Dinos, and throw the Dinos into the goal before they wake up. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/a880dada7be9438037724141f9452dcd.poster.avif?t=1572315748\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/a880dada7be9438037724141f9452dcd.webm?t=1572315748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/a880dada7be9438037724141f9452dcd.mp4?t=1572315748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dinosaur habitats like the Dino-Shore, RAWRcade, and Stock Rex-change will test your skills in single player, or plug in up to 4 more controllers for 5 player coop action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/11306924a372b16ef50dbdd333b26310.poster.avif?t=1572315748\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/745520/extras/11306924a372b16ef50dbdd333b26310.webm?t=1572315